CONCLUSION : DEVOTION TO THE INCARNATE WORD i

150. From all that has been said concerning the role ..Jesus Christ plays in our spiritual life, it follows that in

order to foster this life an intimate, affectionate and habitual union with Him is demanded of us, that is, devotion to the Incarnate Word. " He who abideth in me and I in him, the same beareth much fruit. " 8 The Church brings this

1 / Cor. , XII, 26. 2 Rom. , X, 12 ; 7 Cor. XII, 13. 3 Matth. , XXV, 34-40. * Eph., I, 23. S Pensies, p. 15-16. 6 Coloss. I, 24.

