2 Numerous commentaries facilitate the- understanding of the Psalms. Among the most recent are those of BOYLAN, KISSANE, KNOX and HUGUENY, 0. P., whose object is to give both the literal and spiritual sense in view of the devout recitation of the Divine Office. . ' .

