3 Interior Castle, V Mansion, C. I ; cf. Life, C. XVIII.

- St. Teresa gives the reason why, Interior Castle, V Mansion, C. I : "I dare venture to assert that His Divine Majesty is so joined and united with the essence of the soul, that the devil dare not approach..."

