3 Father FACES, 0. P., in the Histoire de S. V. Ferrier, explains that this was a conditional prophecy, like that of Jonas against Niniveh, and that the world was saved precisely on account of the many conversions the Saint brought about.

4 Supplementary Revelations^ C. XLIX.

s In the Works of Marie Lataste we find among her revelations passages trans- lated from the Summa of St. Thomas. '

