- Mark, XVI, 17. St. Alphonsus Rodriguez was wont to make a large sign of the cross at the moment of the 6bsession and to command the tempter to bow down and' adore Jesus, in virtue of that text of St. Paul -.."That in the name of Jesus every knee should bow,' of those that are in heaven, on earth, and under the earth." (Philip., II, 10). The Saint adds that this put the devil to flight.

